verbose_text: To further validate this hypothesis, the expression of three genes included in the significant data set for biological relevance (AKT1) or highest fold changes (BCL2L1 and SHC1) were analysed in mouse CCs collected from oocytes with different levels of competence based on their post-ovulatory age as shown in Fig. XREF_FIG A (9, 12, 15, 21 and 24 h post-hCG administration).
